Use the provided visualizations to gain insights.

Tools Used

Python (Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn) for data processing and visualization.

Jupyter Notebook for interactive analysis.

GitHub for version control and project sharing.

Future Improvements

Apply machine learning models for purchase prediction.

Integrate real-time data for ongoing analysis.

